com.radiantlogic.iddm.ldap

Class LdapResponse<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radiantlogic.iddm.base.ResponseEntity<T>
      • com.radiantlogic.iddm.ldap.LdapResponse<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The data object type returned with this LdapResponse
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthenticationResponse, CreateResponse, DeleteResponse, HasStatus, ModifyResponse, Response, SearchResponse

    public class LdapResponse<T>
extends ResponseEntity<T>
implements CreateResponse, SearchResponse, ModifyResponse, DeleteResponse, AuthenticationResponse
    Represents an LDAP response containing operation status and any associated data.

    This class wraps LDAP operation results with a status code and optional response data, providing a consistent interface for handling LDAP operation responses.
